Entry.JapaneseText: セレーナさんのコト、夢に見たの？ 心配なのはわかるけど……
Entry.EnglishText: Did you dream about Selena? I can get why you're anxious...

Entry.JapaneseText: ……ちくしょう…… すんげー心配になってきた……
Entry.EnglishText: Damnit... It's made me super anxious...

Entry.JapaneseText: どんな夢だったの？ なんかヒドイ事されてたの？
Entry.EnglishText: What kind of dream was it? Did something terrible happen to her?

Entry.JapaneseText: いや、姉貴がおれの事を置いて、 誰かのところへ行っちまう夢だ。
Entry.EnglishText: Well, I dreamt that she left me behind and went to go be with someone else.

Entry.JapaneseText: それって、お嫁入りなんじゃないの……？
Entry.EnglishText: So basically, you had a dream where she got married?

Entry.JapaneseText: あのさ……セレーナさんは、いつまでも <Tytree>のものじゃないんだからネ。
Entry.EnglishText: Hey now... She's not always going to belong to you, you know.
